The Lean BI System for effective dashboards:

0. Interview Simulation - stakeholder + user 
1. Interview / Notes Evaluation and Follow-up Questions
2. DRD - Dashboard Requirements Document
3. Dashboard Spec 
4. Representation Chooser - Ranked list of representations (Chart / table / KPI) for each component, along with storytelling and context elements and design choices
5. Layout Generator and Component Mapping (wireframe side 1)
6. Wireframe rendering and editing (side 1)
7. Component Scoring - Benefits vs Data cost + effort cost + financial cost (side 2)

